{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-hub-js","path":"/mcgill","result":{"data":{"defaultLogo":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/6d161/sunrise-logo-padded.png","srcSet":"/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/94657/sunrise-logo-padded.png 38w,\n/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/5db04/sunrise-logo-padded.png 75w,\n/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/6d161/sunrise-logo-padded.png 150w,\n/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/7e7e9/sunrise-logo-padded.png 225w,\n/static/b7ed263dd1ded402f44f1342dac6232f/f006c/sunrise-logo-padded.png 246w","sizes":"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px"}}},"defaultHero":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5859030837004404,"src":"/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/7f945/default-hero.jpg","srcSet":"/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/e2788/default-hero.jpg 360w,\n/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/7d509/default-hero.jpg 720w,\n/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/7f945/default-hero.jpg 1440w,\n/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/47dad/default-hero.jpg 2160w,\n/static/829bc32ea4eca8342c578da760275b34/af56c/default-hero.jpg 2880w","sizes":"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px"}}},"events":{"nodes":[]},"hub":{"name":"McGill","about":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center; margin: auto; line-height: 1.3; max-width: 720px; width: 720px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 251);\">Sunrise Movement McGill</h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center; margin: auto; line-height: 1.3; max-width: 720px; width: 720px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 251);\">🍁⚜️🗽&nbsp;</h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center; margin: auto; line-height: 1.3; max-width: 720px; width: 720px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 251);\">Mouvement de Sunrise McGill</h1><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">We are a Montreal-based branch of the Sunrise Movement, associated with our American neighbours. We are a hub of climate leadership and political activism led by young people. Formed in winter 2021, we are focusing our energies on setting up the first-ever hub in the City of Montreal.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Other upcoming plans include joining with other Canadian-based climate justice organizations and creating voter guides for upcoming elections, such as local mayoral races and our student union executive elections.&nbsp;New members are always welcome!</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">If you have experience in grassroots organizing and would like to join our exec team, please email your resume to sunrisemcgill@gmail.com </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Nous sommes une branche du Mouvement Sunrise basé à Montréal, associé à nos voisins Américains. Nous sommes une centre du leadership climatique et de l'activisme politique dirigé par des jeunes. Formée à l'hiver 2021, nous concentrons nos énergies su la mise en place de la toute première filiale Canadienne de Sunrise!</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">D'autres plans à venir comprennent joindre à d'autres organisations de justice climatique basé au Canada, ainsi que la création de guides des électeurs pour les prochaines élections, comme les courses municipales et les courses d'exécutives syndicales des étudiants. Les nouveaux membres sont toujours les bienvenus!</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Si vous avez d'éxpérience dans le milieu de militantisme,  s.v.p. contactez-nous par courier avec votre CV en pièce jointe à sunrisemcgill@Gmail.com</span></p>","email":"sunrisemcgill@gmail.com","website":"https://forms.gle/sUkkHPNaxGd2tAaU9","twitter":"https://twitter.com/sunrisecanada","facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/SunriseMcGill","instagram":"https://www.instagram.com/sunrise.mcgill/","signup":null,"donations":null,"websiteText":"Join us!","logo":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.1875,"src":"/static/a3f4744c3c3059e79684799208fbc305/6d161/logo_1617430608.png.png","srcSet":"/static/a3f4744c3c3059e79684799208fbc305/94657/logo_1617430608.png.png 38w,\n/static/a3f4744c3c3059e79684799208fbc305/5db04/logo_1617430608.png.png 75w,\n/static/a3f4744c3c3059e79684799208fbc305/6d161/logo_1617430608.png.png 150w,\n/static/a3f4744c3c3059e79684799208fbc305/7e7e9/logo_1617430608.png.png 225w,\n/static/a3f4744c3c3059e79684799208fbc305/630fb/logo_1617430608.png.png 300w,\n/static/a3f4744c3c3059e79684799208fbc305/76607/logo_1617430608.png.png 978w","sizes":"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px"}}},"hero":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.8,"src":"/static/d71797de7db8f9f95762137d7b11abd6/35b1e/hero_1617430608.png.png","srcSet":"/static/d71797de7db8f9f95762137d7b11abd6/f4094/hero_1617430608.png.png 360w,\n/static/d71797de7db8f9f95762137d7b11abd6/3c17d/hero_1617430608.png.png 720w,\n/static/d71797de7db8f9f95762137d7b11ab